Using some knowledge about Binary numbers we can find that:
0xxxxxxx  can have min value of 0 and max value of127 to represent that i am using a simple mathematical notation [i,j]= interval including i and j where i is lower bound and j is upper bound.

So, we can modify our representation as:
0xxxxxxx[0,127]
110xxxxx[192,223] 10xxxxxx[128,191]
1110xxxx[224,239] 10xxxxxx[128,191] 10xxxxxx[128,191]
11110xxx[240,247] 10xxxxxx[128,191] 10xxxxxx[128,191] 10xxxxxx[128,191]

